Fergo Close to Signing Colombia, Iraq Contracts, Expansion Says

-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 
2011-04-26T05:37:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/fergo-close-to-signing-colombia-iraq-contracts-expansion-says.html
Fergo Aisa SA (AISA) , a Spanish builder
and real-estate company, is close to signing contracts for
projects in Colombia, Iraq and  Morocco , Expansion reported,
citing Chief Executive Officer Carlos Fernandez.  The contracts will help to keep the company viable,
Fernandez told the newspaper. Fergo has enough assets to
guarantee repayment of 11.5 million euros ($16.7 million)
demanded by lender CatalunyaCaixa through a Spanish court,
Expansion cited Fernandez as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Esteban Duarte in Madrid at 
 eduarterubia@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
